gw.webservice.abcontactapihelpers

Class ABFactory

  • gw.webservice.contactapi.abcontactapihelpers.impl.Factory
    • gw.webservice.abcontactapihelpers.ABFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    _proxy_.gw.lang.reflect.gs.IGosuObject

    public class ABFactory
extends Factory
implements _proxy_.gw.lang.reflect.gs.IGosuObject
    Factory class used by AB to get abcontactapihelpers interface instances to be used when handling ABContactAPI method calls. Generally speaking, the methods in this class match methods in ABContactAPI.
